==Russian==
===Etymology===
Probably from [[не#Russian|не]] + [[ведать]], ‘not to know,’ indicating a strict hands-off relationship.

===Noun===
'''невестка''' (nevéstká) {{f}}

# a woman’s [[daughter-in-law]] ''(husband’s daughter-in-law is [[сноха]])''
# [[sister-in-law]] ''(the wife of one’s brother or brother-in-law)''

